text: Shankar Singh is an Indian politician from the Bharatiya Janata Party and a member of the Rajasthan Legislative Assembly representing the Beawar Vidhan Sabha constituency of Rajasthan. == References == Category:Living people Category:Members of the Rajasthan Legislative Assembly Category:Bharatiya Janata Party politicians from Rajasthan Category:Rajasthan MLAs 2013–2018 Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Shankar Singh (Rajasthan politician)
